headline: 2 Mid-Cap Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 to Avoid
summary: Mid-cap stocks often strike the right balance between having proven business models and market opportunities that can support $100 billion corporations. However, they face intense competition from scaled industry giants and can be disrupted by new innovative players vying for a slice of the pie.

headline: Q1 Earnings Highs And Lows: Packaging Corporation of America (NYSE:PKG) Vs The Rest Of The Industrial Packaging Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q1. Today, we are looking at industrial packaging stocks, starting with Packaging Corporation of America (NYSE:PKG).
